item.title: FOSSASIA and Google Code-in 2015
item.description:
Officially joining the FOSSASIA community with me added to the FOSSASIA Google Code-in 2015 website!! This is my third task and I’m wondering if I can finish 30 quality submissions for a chance for the cough hoodie cough

If you are between 13 and 17 years old you should join Google Code-in right here. Dont hesitate, contributing to the Open Source Community is fun!
